summary: Adds a new race to Skyrim inspired by the demiprince in ESO, this time it is the children of the god of the orcs Malacath.
descriptionHtml:
Long ago in the days following the collapse of their great kingdom there lived a wise women, she tried and struggled to keep her tribe alive in the days after the fall ofÂ orsinium. She prayed to their god to grant her the strength to protect their people from the hatred of the humans and elves that all did seek them dead. The lords of the spurned did take pity upon this woman and her unbreakable mind and resolve, he promised in a vision that if she did lay with him then their child would lead the orcs to salvation.

Adds a new race to the game that is based on the scattered telling of Demiprinces and Demigods in the lore of the Elder Scrolls, enjoy as you destroy your foes with this slightly more pwoerful then normal race with interesting abilities.
author: KyleComments
